 <h2>Hunting Eruds Crossing: Willowwisps</h2><br><br>Eruds Crossing is one of the best places for a Mage to get from 8-12 solo.<br><br>Firstly, to get to Eruds Crossing hop on the boat from Queynos or Erudin, it will stop off at the island in the Erud's Crossing, this is the hunt area of the zone.<br><br><br>From level8 onwards you can hunt even yellow cons, and should be able to take snakes, vampire bats, island madmen, even the undead sailors. The only things that will attack you are the undead and the (rare) fire elemental. However, a few things will assist their friends if you attack them.<br><br><br>When your able, try and take down every Willowisp you see, they are very good exp, and save the Greater Lightstones, they are worth 8pp and some decent exp each in North Karana at the gypsy camp.<br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Zone Information:</u></b><br><br><a href='http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?zone=28'>Erud's Crossing mob list</a><br>
